Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.geolocation.geoip2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeoIP2IPGenerator
    An IP generator that generates IPv4 IPs, based on the IP ranges specified in the CSV format provided by GeoLite2.
    GeoIP2PingERService
    Implements an offline IGeolocationService from the data downloaded from GeoLite2 and PingER.
    GeolocationServiceWithOverrides
    A geolocation service that "wraps" another one.
    LookUpGeoLocationService
    A geo-location service that just looks-up the values in Maps, specified in the constructor.
    OverrideRule
    An immutable class representing an override rule for GeoIP services.
    ResourceUtil
    Utility class for loading resources.
